Breed &amp; Ford (2007), Bryant et al. (2011), Fabre, Fitriana et al. (2017), Menzies (1996), Moore &amp; Burnett (2008), Rimmler (1936), Tate (1951), Thomas (1922c), Watts &amp; Baverstock (1994b), Wood (1971).
</paragraph>
